  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a pan over medium heat.",
    "Add chopped onion, grated ginger, and minced garlic. Saute until the onion turns translucent.",
    "Add chopped potatoes, curry powder, cumin powder, turmeric powder, and salt. Mix well.",
    "Cook for 5-7 minutes, stirring occasionally, until the potatoes start to soften.",
    "Add 2 cups of water and bring to a boil. Reduce the heat to low and simmer for 15-20 minutes or until the potatoes are cooked through.",
